  "properties": {
    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Build a Persona and Problem Statement\r\n\r\nFirst, choose one of the scenarios below to focus on, and create a user persona for it.\r\n* Design an app to help new students make friends at school.\r\n* Design a product to help elderly relatives video call their families more easily.\r\n* Redesign the school cafeteria lunch line to be faster and less chaotic.\r\n\r\nThen, use AI to assist you with the following:\r\n\r\n* **Expand your user persona.**  \r\nAsk AI to help you add realistic details about your user’s schedule, frustrations, and goals.\r\n* **Refine the user’s needs.**  \r\nIdentify what your user really needs, not just tools or features.\r\n* **Write a clear problem statement using the template:**  \r\n_[User] needs a way to [User’s Need] because [Insightful Reason]._\r\n* **Ask AI to review your statement.**  \r\nCheck that it focuses on a need (not a solution) and is specific and user-centered.\r\n* **Record your final version.**  \r\nAdd your best persona and problem statement to your Activity Guide.",
    "offer_browser_tts": "false",
    "submittable": "false",
